title: Crate Break 1.6.1
description:
This fun and addictive puzzle game is about destroying as many boxes at once as you can. To get the best score try to connect boxes of one color by destroying other surrounding ones. Please be wary - after each move the puzzle aligns: firstly all the boxes fall down, then everything is swept to the left! Strategize your moves, play for the score.

Puzzle mode: to unlock next puzzle solve available first.

Break them all!

Game was optimized for HVGA, WVGA and HD screens.

Version 1.6.1:

- 45 new puzzles!
- 2 new game modes: Time Attack and Turbo Mode!
- redesigned interface with new cool graphics and features! 
- many bugfixes.

Unfortunately, due to database optimizations all old higscores are going to be deleted.
